{"tid":1144624,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人等緊5月23日Halo同傳送門合作FPSGame?","createTime":"2019-05-08T07:37:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T04:55:37.000Z","uid":215574,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d1da4aa8d5930b3df80ba978821fe3e45b9f993b","tid":1144624,"uid":215574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T07:37:09.000Z","msg":"【光環加傳送門免費遊戲】Splitgate: Arena Warfare 5月23日免費玩<br />\n<br />\n《分裂之門：競技場戰爭》（Splitgate: Arena Warfare）是一款由1047 Games打造的多人FPS遊戲，本作的玩法結合了《Halo》和《傳送門》系列，採用虛幻4引擎打造。今日官方宣布遊戲將在今年5月23日正式於Steam平台免費發售 <br />\n<br />\n 在本作中，你除了可以體驗到類似《Halo》的傳統FPS快節奏剛槍戰鬥，還可以使用類似《傳送門》的裝備，讓自己穿越傳送門前往戰場上的各種地方，給對手來一次出其不意的襲擊，甚至你還能讓對手從傳送門掉到別處，用戰術技巧贏得勝利。兩者搭配起來，整個遊戲戰場變得更加立體化，戰鬥刺激到停不下來 <br />\nSteam遊戲連結：<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/677620/Splitgate_Arena_Warfare/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F677620%2FSplitgate_Arena_Warfare%2F&d=6Mci4xO0oquEcg2hov7%2FcvYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=48603c7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/677620/Splitgate_Arena_Warfare/</a><br />\nGamePlay<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SadQd1SzCGI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSadQd1SzCGI&d=6Mci4xO0oquEcg2hov7%2FcvYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=ed44de60\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SadQd1SzCGI</a>"},{"pid":"a3125495ff5c5bc6825fca0a0b70e48081aeac6e","tid":1144624,"uid":176802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T07:38:06.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"4a8772c351c3a9db84ba02c7d4f6898cdc83cd4d","tid":1144624,"uid":215574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3125495ff5c5bc6825fca0a0b70e48081aeac6e","tid":1144624,"uid":176802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T07:38:06.000Z","msg":"冇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T07:42:28.000Z","msg":"睇完有冇小小興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo